== 遊戲設計 ==
在格鬥遊戲中，角色之間使用高度誇張的武打動作交手。<ref name="fundamentals" />遊戲類型一般主要以人物纷争或{{tsl|en|Combat sport|技擊運動}}为話題，<ref name="ashcraft90" /><ref name="xboxguide" />有些以武器對戰為特色。<ref name="xboxguide" />通常以側面視點顯示出螢幕上的角色，即使3D格鬥遊戲大部分也以2D平面動作進行。<ref name="fundamentals" />遊戲通常侷限角色左右移動及跳躍，某些遊戲如《[[饿狼传说系列|餓狼傳說]]》允許角色進行水平移動（換線）。<ref name="fundamentals" /><ref name="gamespotfatal">{{cite web |author=Provo, Frank |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/wii/action/fatalfury/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Fatal Fury: King of Fighters Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2007-10-11 |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120707175927/http://uk.gamespot.com/wii/action/fatalfury/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |archivedate=2012-07-07 }}</ref>2000年[[育碧|育碧]]推出的3D械斗游戏《[[汤姆和杰瑞之毛绒之拳|汤姆和杰瑞之毛绒之拳]]》(''Tom & Jerry in Fists of Furry'')允许玩家向四个方向自由移动，还允许玩家拾取和更换武器<ref>{{cite web |author=Gin_Tama |title=Tom and Jerry in Fists of Furry |url=http://www.gamespot.com/tom-and-jerry-in-fists-of-furry-2000/user-reviews/2200-532194/ |publisher=GameSpot |date=2006-06-26 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |archive-date=2017-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303051048/http://www.gamespot.com/tom-and-jerry-in-fists-of-furry-2000/user-reviews/2200-532194/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但限制了武器的使用次数，也没有格斗招数的设定。新的遊戲傾向於[[渲染|渲染]]三維效果並允許「{{nihongo|短跳躍|ステップ|side-stepping}}」，但其他方面的遊戲進行則像是二維渲染。<ref name="xboxguide" />

<!-- 注释出：[[File:Tekken_Xiaoyu01.jpg|thumb]]5》的跳躍攻擊]] -->
除了圍繞著有限空間移動，格鬥遊戲对玩家招式的限制使其采取不同的進攻和防守策略。玩家必須經過反覆的[[试错|试错]]练习，才能了解哪些攻擊和防守方式能有效對抗敵手。<ref name="fundamentals" />玩家可用{{nihongo|防禦|ガード|blocking}}招式抵禦對手的攻擊。<ref name="50VF">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-virtua-fighter |title=The Essential 50: Virtua Fighter |publisher=1UP |accessdate=2009-01-30 |archive-date=2012-07-19 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120719110526/http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-virtua-fighter |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些遊戲设计了更高級的防禦技巧，例如卡普空《[[快打旋風III|快打旋風III]]》的「{{nihongo|格擋|ブロッキング|parrying}}」能使玩家避开攻击伤害且在短时间内使攻擊的一方无法采取行为应对（在[[SNK_Playmore|SNK]]的《[[餓狼－群狼之證|餓狼－群狼之證]]》中也有类似招式设定，但称其为「瞬防（just defended）」）。<ref>{{cite web |author=Gerstmann, Jeff |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/dreamcast/action/streetfighter3doubleimpact/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Street Fighter III: Double Impact Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=1999-12-29 |accessdate=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120715010218/http://uk.gamespot.com/dreamcast/action/streetfighter3doubleimpact/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |archivedate=2012-07-15 }}</ref><ref name="ignfatal">{{cite web |author=Chau, Anthony |url=http://uk.dreamcast.ign.com/articles/166/166258p1.html |title=Fatal Review: Mark of the Wolves |publisher=IGN |date=2001-12-11 |accessdate=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007042313/http://uk.dreamcast.ign.com/articles/166/166258p1.html |archivedate=2008-10-07 }}</ref>在拳打腳踢不奏效时，玩家可以使用{{tsl|en|Throw (grappling)|投擲}}或摔技克制對手的「防禦」招式。反过来，投掷技能又受普通拳脚的克制。預測對手的動作並反擊，稱為「反制」，是[[游戏性|遊戲互動]]的一個普遍元素。<ref name="xboxguide">{{cite web |author=Treit, Ryan |url=http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/tips/noviceguides/fighting.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515013224/http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/tips/noviceguides/fighting.htm |archivedate=2009-05-15 |title=Novice Guides: Fighting |publisher=Xbox.com |accessdate=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>格鬥遊戲中不同高度的跳躍攻擊所造成的傷害也往往有所差異。<ref name="essential50">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-street-fighter-ii |title=The Essential 50: 32. Street Fighter II |publisher=1UP |accessdate=2009-01-15 |archive-date=2012-07-20 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120720141819/http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-street-fighter-ii |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Ekberg, Brian |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/ds/action/k1worldgp/news.html?sid=6179720&mode=previews&tag=result;title;0 |title=TGS '07: K-1 World Grand Prix Hands-On |publisher=GameSpot |date=2007-09-22 |accessdate=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120715174733/http://uk.gamespot.com/ds/action/k1worldgp/news.html?sid=6179720&mode=previews&tag=result;title;0 |archivedate=2012-07-15 }}</ref>因此及时預測對手的招式甚為重要，就像是[[剪刀、石頭、布|剪刀、石頭、布]]。<ref name="fundamentals" />

===特殊攻擊===
格鬥遊戲的一项特色就是「特殊攻擊」（或稱“隱藏招式”或“必杀技”）的设计，<ref name="essential50" />玩家必须按下複雜的組合按鍵才能将其招式发出来。<ref>{{cite web |author=Towell, Justin |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/the-best-special-attacks-ever/ |title=The Best Special Attacks Ever |publisher=GamesRadar |accessdate=2009-01-29 |archive-date=2012-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126204346/http://www.gamesradar.com/the-best-special-attacks-ever/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>必杀技的设定最早源于日本遊戲公司[[SNK|SNK]]的《[[龙虎之拳|龙虎之拳]]》。<ref>{{cite news |author="罗马企鹅" |title=盘点格斗游戏史上的必杀技TOP10 |url=http://tv.17173.com/news/07042016/205835491.shtml |publisher=17173.com |date=2016-07-04 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |quote="《龙虎拳》里的霸王翔吼拳是格斗史上第一个必杀，必杀技的概念就是从这款游戏中诞生的。" |archive-date=2017-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303043515/http://tv.17173.com/news/07042016/205835491.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>不过多数“必杀技”在游戏中并不能真的做到“一击必杀”。自《街頭霸王II》發行後，透過基本拳腳攻擊達成多重連續攻擊的連段方式，已經成為格鬥遊戲另一項不可或缺的基本特徵。<ref name="edge">{{cite journal |year=2003 |title=The making of ''Street Fighter II'' |journal=Edge presents Retro |issue='The Making of...' Special |quote="[Combos] became the base for future fighting titles"}}</ref>一些格鬥遊戲會显示「连击数」以表示玩家連段的進展。完成连击可以获得更高分数评价，其成败通常和连招施展難度及不小心扑空的风险程度相關。练习发动连招往往超越[[休閒遊戲|休閒遊戲]]玩家的能力，需要同時擁有卓越的記憶力和掌握優秀時機的反應力。<ref name="fundamentals" />「嘲諷」动作是某些遊戲的另一項特色，由SNK的《[[龍虎之拳|龍虎之拳]]》最早引進。<ref>''Arcade Mania!'', pp. 100–101.</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Park, Andrew |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/ps2/action/artoffightinganthology/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Art of Fighting Anthology Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2007-06-05 |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120717135451/http://uk.gamespot.com/ps2/action/artoffightinganthology/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |archivedate=2012-07-17 }}</ref>嘲讽可用來增加遊戲幽默樂趣，但也有增進角色攻擊強度的效果。<ref>{{cite web |author=Rose, Martyn |url=http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/k/kungfuchaos/themakers5.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205175426/http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/k/kungfuchaos/themakers5.htm |archivedate=2008-12-05 |title=Designing Kung-Fu Chaos, Part 3 |publisher=Xbox.com |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>有的角色的嘲諷动作会引起玩家的特别注意，例如《[[快打旋風ZERO系列|快打旋風ZERO]]》的{{tsl|en|Dan Hibiki|火引彈}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/top-20-street-fighter-characters-of-all-time/?page=3 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301120425/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/top-20-street-fighter-characters-of-all-time/?page=3 |archivedate=2009-03-01 |title=Top 20 Street Fighter Characters of All Time |publisher=[[GameDaily|GameDaily]] |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/top-25-most-bizarre-fighting-characters/?page=24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206220705/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/top-25-most-bizarre-fighting-characters/?page=24 |archivedate=2009-02-06 |title=Top 25 Most Bizarre Fighting Characters |publisher=[[GameDaily|GameDaily]] |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

===回合競賽===
格鬥遊戲競賽通常由數個回合構成（一般為三戰兩勝）；勝利回合數最多的玩家贏得比賽。<ref>{{cite web |author=Kasavin, Greg |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/ps2/action/capcomfightingjam/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Capcom Fighting Jam Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2004-11-16 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010111303/http://uk.gamespot.com/capcom-fighting-evolution/reviews/capcom-fighting-evolution-review-6113212/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>以醒目的血条（或称“血槽”）展示人物[[生命值|生命值]]是格鬥遊戲普遍特徵之一，當角色遭受攻擊時會变少。<ref name="gamespotfatal" /><ref>{{cite web |author=Staff |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/making-japans-first-rpg |title=The Making of... Japan's First RPG |publisher=Edge Online |date=2008-03-06 |accessdate=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120125093639/http://www.next-gen.biz/features/making-japans-first-rpg |archivedate=2012-01-25 }}</ref>每次成功的攻擊都會耗損受攻击角色的生命值，直到其中一方生命值為零才宣告回合結束。<ref name="fundamentals" />因此遊戲的主要目的在完全削減對手的血條，達成「[[擊倒|擊倒]]」对方的结局。<ref name="ignfatal" />自[[Midway|Midway]]1992年推出的《[[真人快打|真人快打]]》開始，《真人快打系列》的勝利者皆以陰森的表現方式擊倒對手。<ref name="MK3">{{cite web |author=Gertsmann, Jeff |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/ultimatemortalkombat3/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Ultimate Mortal Kombat 3 Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2008-10-24 |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711071814/https://uk.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/ultimatemortalkombat3/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary%3Bread-review |archivedate=2011-07-11 }}</ref>《[[VR快打系列|VR快打]]》之類的遊戲允許角色以被推出比賽場地的方式擊敗，裁定「場外犯規」。<ref name="50VF" />回合的判決也可以由時間結束時決定（若有計時），將裁定剩餘血量較多的一方為勝者。格鬥遊戲一般含有單人玩家戰役或聯賽，玩家必需連續打敗多名電腦控制的敵手。聯賽勝利後通常會揭示一段特別故事結局的[[剧情画面|剧情画面]]，某些遊戲会在通关后奖励玩家使用隱藏角色或特殊功能的權限。<ref name="DOA4">{{cite web |author=Kasavin, Greg |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/deadoralive4/review.html |title=Dead or Alive 4 Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2006-01-01 |accessdate=2009-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130135142/http://uk.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/deadoralive4/review.html |archivedate=2009-01-30 }}</ref>

===選擇角色===
在大多數格鬥遊戲，玩家可以從多種具有獨特戰鬥風格和特殊招式的角色中選擇。自《街頭霸王II》後這成為了此類型游戏的牢固慣例，而角色的選擇帶來更深層次的博弈策略和[[重玩價值|重玩價值]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/sfhistory/games_02_02.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040902095224/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/sfhistory/games_02_02.html |archivedate=2004-09-02 |title=GameSpot: The History of Street Fighter – Street Fighter II: The World Warriors |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=2009-04-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>格鬥遊戲也提供女性角色，但形象通常趨於過度強調其性別特徵，並且将其刊登在遊戲雜誌的[[海報女郎|封面女郎]]作為宣传噱头。全世界第一個在格鬥遊戲中登場的而可以供玩家操作的女性角色是 張[[春麗|春麗]]/Chun Li《街頭霸王Il》。<ref>{{cite book |title=Rules of Play: Game Design Fundamentals |url=https://archive.org/details/rulesplaygamedes00sale |author=Katie Salen, Eric Zimmerman |publisher=MIT Press |year=2003 |isbn=0-262-24045-9 |page=[https://archive.org/details/rulesplaygamedes00sale/page/n650 526]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Most Attractive Female Fighters From Popular Games|url=http://www.gamesreviews2010.com/most-attractive-female-fighters-from-popular-games/|accessdate=2015-03-12|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714022126/http://www.gamesreviews2010.com/most-attractive-female-fighters-from-popular-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>男性角色往往具有寬厚胸膛和肩膀、堅實肌肉和突出的下巴。<ref name="fundamentals" />部分遊戲允許訂製角色，讓玩家可以改變角色的外觀或招式組合。《{{tsl|ja|スーパーファイヤープロレスリングX|超級火焰職業摔角X}}》是第一款擁有這項功能的遊戲。<ref>{{cite book |editor=Craig Glenday |title=Guinness World Records Gamer's Edition 2008 |url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0 |series=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]] |date=2008-03-11 |publisher=Guinness |isbn=978-1-904994-21-3 |page=[https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0/page/84 84] |chapter=Record-Breaking Games}}</ref>而在後來的《{{tsl|ja|2D格闘ツクール2nd.|2D格鬥遊戲工具}}》<ref>{{cite web |author=Craig Harris |title=Fighter Maker review |url=http://uk.psx.ign.com/articles/153/153775p1.html |date=1999-06-17 |accessdate=2007-07-22 |publisher=IGN |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017031726/http://uk.psx.ign.com/articles/153/153775p1.html |archivedate=2007-10-17 }}</ref>、《[[劍魂III|劍魂III]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://palgn.com.au/article.php?id=3356 |title=Soulcalibur III Review |accessdate=2007-07-22 |publisher=PALGN |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070909161129/http://www.palgn.com.au/article.php?id=3356 |archivedate=2007-09-09 }}</ref>、《{{tsl|en|Mortal Kombat: Armageddon|真人快打：末日戰場}}》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamingtarget.com/article.php?artid=5037 |title=Mortal Kombat screens and Create-A-Fighter details |accessdate=2007-07-22 |publisher=Gaming Target |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927201747/http://www.gamingtarget.com/article.php?artid=5037 |dead-url=no }}</ref>等遊戲也都採用了這個概念。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/dragon-ball-z-tenkaichi-neo/725582p2.html |title=Dragon Ball Z Budokai 3(PS2) preview |accessdate=2007-07-22 |publisher=GameSpy |archive-date=2007-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016073855/http://uk.ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/dragon-ball-z-tenkaichi-neo/725582p2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>某些對戰遊戲允許玩家創造有別於原版遊戲內容的元素，例如《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥X|任天堂明星大亂鬥X]]》能夠建立自訂舞台。<ref name="ignsmash">{{cite web |author=Casamassina, Matt |url=http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/856/856580p3.html |title=Super Smash Bros. Brawl Review |publisher=IGN |date=2008-03-04 |accessdate=2009-01-31 |archive-date=2009-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207092541/http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/856/856580p3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===多人模式===
部分格鬥遊戲也可提供多人模式讓玩家互別苗頭，有時是讓第二位玩家在第一位玩家進行單人模式時隨時可以插入挑戰。<ref name="ashcraft90" />少數作品允許最多4名玩家同時競爭。<ref name="gamespotsmash">{{cite web |author=Anderson, Lark |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/wii/action/supersmashbros/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |title=Super Smash Bros. Brawl Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2008-03-08 |accessdate=2009-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210125316/http://uk.gamespot.com/wii/action/supersmashbros/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary%3Bread-review |archivedate=2009-02-10 }}</ref>一些遊戲具有特別的「搭檔組隊」模式，雖然對戰仍是一對一，但角色可以從舞台中離開，由另一名隊友替換。<ref>{{cite web |author=Zdyrko, David |url=http://uk.ps2.ign.com/articles/163/163946p1.html |title=Tekken Tag Tournament |publisher=IGN |date=2000-10-23 |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-date=2008-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080211230621/http://uk.ps2.ign.com/articles/163/163946p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>部分格鬥遊戲還提供[[車輪戰|車輪戰]]的挑戰模式，以測試玩家的持久力。<ref name="DOA4" />較新的作品具備了線上遊戲服務的優勢，雖然緩慢[[数据传输|数据传输]]的[[延遲_(電腦)|延遲]]會造成對戰的開始瞬間不同時。<ref name="DOA4" /><ref>''Arcade Mania!'', p. 108.</ref>延遲造成的影響可以通过使用{{tsl|en|GGPO}}技術得到減緩。這項技術通过快速回溯至最近精確的遊戲狀態、校正錯誤、再跳回當前影格等步骤，令遊戲得以保持同步。使用該技術的作品有《[[骷髏少女|骷髏少女]]》和《{{tsl|en|Street Fighter III: 3rd Strike|快打旋風III 3rd STRIKE}}》。<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2011-04-23|url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/34050/Interview_How_A_Fighting_Game_Fan_Solved_Internet_Latency_Issues.php|title=Interview: How A Fighting Game Fan Solved Internet Latency Issues|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|archive-date=2011-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110425150653/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34050/Interview_How_A_Fighting_Game_Fan_Solved_Internet_Latency_Issues.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://shoryuken.com/2011/06/06/street-fighter-iii-3rd-strike-online-1st-trailer-and-screens/ |title=Street Fighter III: 3rd Strike Online – 1st Trailer and Screens |first=Adam |last=Heart |date=2011-06-06 |work=Shoryuken |accessdate=2011-06-06 |quote=Street Fighter III Third Strike Online Edition will be using GGPO netcode ... |archive-date=2011-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608025320/http://shoryuken.com/2011/06/06/street-fighter-iii-3rd-strike-online-1st-trailer-and-screens/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==遊戲技巧==
格鬥遊戲對打擊回饋有一定要求，通常不會有被敵方成功攻擊後無反應或成功攻擊敵方，敵方卻無反應的情況發生(技能無敵、霸體效果除外)，進而考驗雙方先後手、格檔、閃避、使用招式的技巧。

格鬥遊戲對於雙方動作的對應和判斷比起大多數的[[動作遊戲|動作遊戲]]還來的高，像是招式相殺、攻擊判定高低、壩體、防禦、投技、格反等技巧判定，因此格鬥遊戲對防禦或閃避等避免讓自己損失生命值的技巧，都是設計成無冷卻但有防禦條或其他限制方式，來保持格鬥遊戲的流暢感並維持其高技術性需求。

攻擊方式也是同理，攻擊動作通常不會有冷卻時間的條件，而是用能量條來做限制，但也是有例外。
而有加入冷卻時間的動作，該動作進入冷卻時間後使用，但會有使用「失敗動作」的動作做為懲罰(例如槍會顯示開槍動作，但卻沒有子彈射出)，來保持格鬥遊戲的流暢感並維持其高技術性需求。

